    About Terminal Artist Space

    TerminalDAO (Terminal Artists Space), established as a decentralized autonomous organization in the year 2021 with the goal of bringing together traditional artists and XR artists around web3, today gathers artists, designers, architects, and software developers through disruptive technologies to foster sustainable-regenerative production in industries and raise awareness about the climate crisis.

    The artwork has been hand-drawned by Robert Green in the traditional anime style and composited by Layla Efiyo.
